robeur m (plural robeurs)

  1. rubber; product of the rubber tree or similar latex, or its synthetic analogues
    Synonym: caoutchouc
  2. tire, tyre; vulcanized rubber pneumatic tires of automotive vehicles
    Synonym: pneu
trans: product of the rubber tree or similar latex, or its synthetic analogues
vulcanized rubber pneumatic tires of automotive vehicles
